Kenya Breweries Limited's flagship brand Tusker recently hosted a rhumba night at Summerland Hotel in Nakuru. Rhumba lovers flocked the venue for an all-night episode of Sensa Muzika band assisted by radio presenter Nick Odhiambo, who doubled up as the MC. DJ Marto Sibuor offered a thrilling set that kept the revellers on their feet all through the night. The party acted as the third edition of the Tusker Grill masters following a successful second edition held at Thika, where they hosted a Mugithi street party and launched the campaign ‘I love beer’.